Hello there.  This is Sean Sulham and this is my proposal.
The theme is pizza.
The use cases are the following:
   Finding the closest pizza place
   Inter-Pizza Comparisons (Comparing Pizza Restaurants)
   Intra-Pizza Comparisons (Comparing Pizzas within a particular 
restaurant)
	Comparing by price, picture, service, customer popularity, and 
customer reviews
   Post customer reviews on your favorite (or least favorite) pizza 
experiences
   Cast your votes for the best pizza
   Post pics of your best homemade pizza
   Search for best specialty pizzerias:
      Ex: NY Style, Chicago Deep Dish, Authentic Italian
